com.codename1.webrtc

Interface RTCVideoElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventTarget, RTCElement, RTCMediaElement

    public interface RTCVideoElement
extends RTCMediaElement

    The RTCVideoElement interface provides special properties and methods for manipulating video objects. It also inherits properties and methods of RTCMediaElement and RTCElement.

    The list of supported media formats varies from one browser to the other. You should either provide your video in a single format that all the relevant browsers supports, or provide multiple video sources in enough different formats that all the browsers you need to support are covered.

    See Also:
    https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement
